Description:
Before you lies the wreckage of the Dreadnought, the flagship of the feared captain known as Halfman. The ship is gargantuan, but it lies broken beyond repair. 

You marvel at how they were ever capable of constructing such a colossal vessel—it's the pinnacle of shipbuilding!

There is a large hole in the hull through which you might enter, provided you can clear away the planks and debris blocking it.
